text: Leiosyrinx liphaima is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Raphitomidae.MolluscaBase (2019). MolluscaBase. Leiosyrinx liphaima Bouchet & Sysoev, 2001. Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species at: http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id;=434201 on 2019-07-24 ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species was found in deep water in the Coral Sea. ==References== * Bouchet, P. & Sysoev, A., 2001.
